______________________________________________________________________ _______ 33 National Coral Reef Action Strategy GOAL 4: UNDERSTAND SOCIAL AND ECONOMIC FACTORS KEY THREATS ADDRESSED Understanding the value and human use of coral reefs ( i.e. social and economic factors) is critical to reducing threats to coral reef ecosystems.
The figure below is a general summary of the relative importance (H = high, M = medium, L = low) of this goal in addressing the impacts of key threats.
