Ã¯Â¿Â½ Ã¯Â¿Â½ ______________________________________________________________________ _______ 46 National Coral Reef Action Strategy GOAL 6: REDUCE ADVERSE IMPAC TS OF FISHING AND OTHER EXTRACTIVE USES KEY THREATS ADDRESSED: Reducing the adverse impacts of fishing and other extractive uses is critical to reducing key threats to coral reef ecosystems.
