______________________________________________________________________ _______ 73 National Coral Reef Action Strategy GOAL 10: IMPROVE OUTREACH AND EDUCATION KEY THREATS ADDRESSED: Improving outreach and education is critical to helping people understand the value of coral reef ecosystems and how to avoid damaging them.
Outreach and education are an essential part of fulfilling all the other goals in this strategy, and therefore address a number of key threats to coral reef ecosystems.
The figure below is a genera l summary of the relative importance (H = high, M = medium, L = low) of this goal area (outreach and education) in addressing the impacts from these threats.
