______________________________________________________________________ _______ 78 National Coral Reef Action Strategy GOAL 11: REDUCE THREATS TO INTE RNATIONAL CORAL REEFS KEY THREATS ADDRESSED: Reducing international threats to coral reefs requires addressing a number of issues critical to the long- term protection of coral reef ecosystems.
The figure below is a general summary of the relative importance (H = high, M = medium, L = low) of this goal in addressing the impacts from these threats.
