______________________________________________________________________ _______ 84 National Coral Reef Action Strategy GOAL 12: REDUCE IMPACTS FROM INTERNATIONAL TRADE IN CORAL REEF RESOURCES KEY THREATS ADDRESSED: Reducing impacts from international trade is important to reducing a number of key threats to coral reef ecosystems.
The figure below is a general summary of the relative importance (H = high, M = medium, L = low) of this goal in addressing the impacts from these threats.
